 debug entry sequencing\n   - Returns detailed error messages for troubleshooting\n\n4. **Task 4: MergeTasks Function** ✅\n   - Implemented `MergeTasks(tasks)` function\n   - Validates no duplicate task IDs\n   - Returns merged task list\n   - Handles empty task lists gracefully\n\n5. **Task 5: Caching Mechanism** ✅\n   - Implemented thread-safe caching using `sync.RWMutex`\n   - Cache is automatically populated on first load\n   - Subsequent loads return cached results\n   - Provided `ClearCache()` and `ClearAllCache()` functions\n   - Prevents redundant file I/O and parsing\n\n#### Additional Features Implemented\n\n- **GetTaskByID()**: Retrieve specific task from context\n- **GetDebugEntriesByTaskID()**: Get debug entries related to a task\n- **GetSummaryStats()**: Generate statistics about job context\n- **Circular Dependency Detection**: DFS-based algorithm to detect cycles\n- **Thread-Safe Operations**: All cache operations use mutex locks\n\n#### Test Coverage\n\n**Test File**: `internal/parser/coordinator_test.go`\n- **Total Tests**: 18 comprehensive test cases\n- **Coverage**: 67.4% of statements\n- **All Tests Passing**: ✅\n\n**Test Categories**:\n1. Coordinator initialization\n2. Single-file loading\n3. Multi-file loading\n4. Cache functionality (load, clear, clear-all)\n5. Consistency validation (valid, undefined deps, circular deps)\n6. Task merging (success, duplicates, empty)\n7. Task lookup\n8. Summary statistics\n9. Debug entry retrieval\n10. Circular dependency detection (self-ref, long chains)\n\n#### Integration Verification\n\n- **Full Parser Test Suite**: 85 tests pass ✅\n- **Build Verification**: Code compiles without errors ✅\n- **Backward Compatibility**: All existing tests still pass ✅\n\n### Key Design Decisions\n\n1. **Thread-Safe Caching**: Used `sync.RWMutex` for concurrent access safety\n2. **Graceful File Handling**: Missing files don't cause errors, just empty structures\n3. **Circular Dependency Detection**: Implemented DFS algorithm for robust cycle detection\n4. **Separation of Concerns**: Coordinator focuses on orchestration, not parsing\n5. **Extensibility**: Easy to add new file types or validation rules\n\n### Validation Results\n\n| Criterion | Status | Details |\n|-----------|--------|---------|\n| LoadJobContext() loads all files | ✅ | Verified with multi-file test |\n| Consistency checking works | ✅ | Detects undefined deps & cycles |\n| Task merging works | ✅ | Handles duplicates & empty lists |\n| Caching mechanism | ✅ | Thread-safe, LRU-friendly |\n| Unit test coverage | ✅ | 18 tests, 67.4% coverage |\n| Integration | ✅ | All 85 parser tests pass |\n| Build | ✅ | Compiles without errors |\n\n### Files Modified/Created\n\n- ✅ Created: `internal/parser/coordinator.go` (300 lines)\n- ✅ Created: `internal/parser/coordinator_test.go` (400 lines)\n- ✅ Updated: `.morty/plan/parser.md` (Job 5 marked complete)\n- ✅ Committed: All changes to git\n\n### Loop Statistics\n\n- **Loop Count**: 1\n- **Tasks Completed**: 5/5 (100%)\n- **Debug Issues**: 0\n- **Explore Subagent Used**: No\n- **Plan File Updated**: Yes ✅\n\n---\n\n**Summary**: Job 5 successfully implements a production-ready multi-file parsing coordinator with comprehensive validation, thread-safe caching, and 18 passing tests. All validator criteria met. Ready for integration with dag_executor and prompt_manager modules.\n\nEOF\n"},"name":"Bash","id":"toolu_bdrk_01Le8ugPuFuYt3TVEWzHAY1e","type":"tool_use"}],"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b05d876d-a988-4fa2-9008-5d8aa9eb341b","uuid":"06230501-3243-4116-8032-71affb71a185"},{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Le8ugPuFuYt3TVEWzHAY1e","type":"tool_result","content":"## RALPH_STATUS - Job 5 Completion Summary\n\n**Module**: parser\n**Job**: 多文件解析协调器 (Multi-file Parsing Coordinator)\n**Status**: COMPLETED ✅\n\n### Implementation Summary\n\n#### Deliverables (All 5 Tasks Completed)\n\n1. **Task 1: Coordinator Co